        "value": "1.1 Recruitment of national consultant (Digital Agri Consultant)1.2 Stock taking and Scoping study1.3 organization of meetings and consultations of technical and steering committees1.4 Drafting of strategic action plan linking with digital framework 20192.1 Develop a DV platform with a detailed business model in target areas2.2 Identification and assessment of the farms for the DVI3.1 Establish digitally enabled community hub3.2 Assess digital technology, skill required for farmers and other stakeholders3.3 Support enabling conditions to access, use and deploy digital services by public and support services (service providers)3.4 Operationalize DVI platform to increase access to digital tools and technologies and build skills in protocols and tools3.5 Conduct exposure visit (study tour) of concerned government officials to Bangladesh3.6 Conduct training to concerned stakeholders on DVI3.7 Conduct co-designing workshop with farmers, cooperatives and local service providers and market actors on DV business model3.8 Documentation and dissemination of best practices and success cases3.9 Development of a project framework for upscaling"
